lastfm.summary: “Woman”, the second single from Little Simz’s sophomore album "Sometimes I Might Be Introvert", is a track in homage to the women that inspire Simz on the daily. Woven into the showers of compliments and praise are several allusions to largely populated areas of people of colour, including many countries throughout Africa, as well as Jamaica, India, and Brooklyn, New York. "This was made to uplift and celebrate women. To my peers, my family Read more on Last.fm.
lastfm.title: Woman
